  <summary date="2023-02-16T17:24:28Z" status="Introduced in House">Return Home to Housing Act

This bill increases the maximum rate of per diem payments provided by the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to entities (i.e., grant recipients or authorized entities) that furnish services and transitional housing to homeless veterans. The bill also specifies that the VA may adjust the per diem rate in response to an emergency.</summary>
